  "detailed_description": "Start with four basic elements and combine them to create over 400 unique items. Each discovery brings you closer to mastering the art of alchemy.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2661530/extras/321fd367af350678ca0be80ec2939950.poster.avif?t=1732084803\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2661530/extras/321fd367af350678ca0be80ec2939950.webm?t=1732084803\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2661530/extras/321fd367af350678ca0be80ec2939950.mp4?t=1732084803\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>With intuitive gameplay and a simple interface, this game encourages creativity and logical thinking as you experiment with different combinations. Whether you're new to alchemy or a seasoned pro, Alchemy Origins offers a satisfying challenge for all puzzle enthusiasts.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2661530/extras/18313b07cb35435be8f3ef3c5263ae28.poster.avif?t=1732084803\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2661530/extras/18313b07cb35435be8f3ef3c5263ae28.webm?t=1732084803\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2661530/extras/18313b07cb35435be8f3ef3c5263ae28.mp4?t=1732084803\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Combine 4 basic elements to create 400+ unique items<br></li><li>Intuitive, easy-to-learn gameplay<br></li><li>Explore increasingly complex puzzles</li></ul><br>Create your path to alchemical mastery in <strong>Alchemy Origins!</strong>",
  "about_the_game": "Start with four basic elements and combine them to create over 400 unique items. Each discovery brings you closer to mastering the art of alchemy.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2661530/extras/321fd367af350678ca0be80ec2939950.poster.avif?t=1732084803\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2661530/extras/321fd367af350678ca0be80ec2939950.webm?t=1732084803\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2661530/extras/321fd367af350678ca0be80ec2939950.mp4?t=1732084803\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>With intuitive gameplay and a simple interface, this game encourages creativity and logical thinking as you experiment with different combinations. Whether you're new to alchemy or a seasoned pro, Alchemy Origins offers a satisfying challenge for all puzzle enthusiasts.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2661530/extras/18313b07cb35435be8f3ef3c5263ae28.poster.avif?t=1732084803\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2661530/extras/18313b07cb35435be8f3ef3c5263ae28.webm?t=1732084803\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2661530/extras/18313b07cb35435be8f3ef3c5263ae28.mp4?t=1732084803\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Combine 4 basic elements to create 400+ unique items<br></li><li>Intuitive, easy-to-learn gameplay<br></li><li>Explore increasingly complex puzzles</li></ul><br>Create your path to alchemical mastery in <strong>Alchemy Origins!</strong>"